#: incl/customizer/class-lafka-customizer-abandoned-cart.php:168
msgid "How long the cart must be idle (no order placed) before the recovery email fires. WP-Cron checks the queue every 15 minutes, so the actual send happens within (delay + 15) minutes of abandonment."
